  <brief_title>Efficacy of Everolimus in Combination With Tacrolimus in Liver Transplant Recipients</brief_title>
  <acronym>HEPHAISTOS</acronym>
  <official_title>A 12-month, Multi-center, Open-label, Randomized, Controlled Study to Evaluate Efficacy/Safety and Evolution of Renal Function of Everolimus in Co-exposure With Tacrolimus in de Novo Liver Transplant Recipients</official_title>
