  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Eestimated glomerular filtration rate (MDRD-4 formula) at Month 12 in de novo liver</measure>
    <time_frame>at 12 months after randomization</time_frame>
    <description>Immunosuppressive regimen based on everolimus (EVR) in coexposure with tacrolimus (TAC) compared to tacrolimus alone on estimated glomerular filtration rate (MDRD-4 formula) at Month 12 in de novo liver transplant recipients.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
